    <sect1 id="zend.locale.appendix.numberscripts">
        <title>Supported number notations in Zend_Locale_Format::toNumberSystem()</title>
        <para>
            <code>Zend_Locale_Format::toNumberSystem()</code> 
            can normalize, localize and convert numbers between different scripts.
        </para>
